'''Rakati''' was the capital city of the planet [[Ksift]]. It was in a downtown alley of this city where [[Bret Hanson]] managed to capture the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] traitor [[Nik (Rebel)|Nik]] after a brief stunt with a [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]].

